    <item>
      <title>特朗普上台威胁州和地方政府减税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普竞选第二任总统的势头再次引发了人们的担忧，即长期以来的市政债券税收减免可能会被取消，以帮助支付永久性减税的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/trump-s-rise-threatens-tax-break-for-state-and-local-governments</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 16:15:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德巩固巨头地位；高盛业绩好坏参半</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-15/blackrock-cements-behemoth-status-goldman-results-mixed-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街收益推动了今天“彭博未平仓合约”华尔街热点话题的讨论，Sonali Basak、Matthew Miller 和 Katie Greifeld 分析了贝莱德公司的最新表现。该公司管理的资产超过了富达、资本集团、富兰克林邓普顿和景顺的总和。与此同时，高盛集团的业绩喜忧参半。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-07-15/blackrock-cements-behemoth-status-goldman-results-mixed-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 15:07:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价在夏季交易中波动，焦点是中国数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员评估了美国和中国需求低迷的迹象，油价几乎没有变化，而随着市场消化了对唐纳德·特朗普的攻击并展望收益，股市上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-july-15</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 23:29:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔讲话后股市上涨，大选焦虑消退：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普遭遇暗杀袭击增加了他入主白宫的可能性，但有关市场波动加剧的呼声并未成为现实，股市因此上涨至历史新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-waver-as-traders-juggle-trump-win-bets-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:18:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着“特朗普交易”的兴起，美国股市上涨，小型股上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-steady-as-traders-digest-latest-geopolitial-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者权衡周末唐纳德·特朗普遇袭事件对市场的影响并期待本周的财报热潮，美国股市周一飙升至新高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/us-futures-steady-as-traders-digest-latest-geopolitial-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
